      "content": "A gritty detective would logically suspect the \"tough darks\" or local Irish gangatics who hate outsiders and patrol these run-down blocks to protect their turf. Our streets, which we've worked so hard to build into a dictatorship, run beautiful, and it was just a matter of time before a resident got knocked down. The most realistic lead is a local union man or a corrupt cop who absorbs the provenance for this city's unspeakable poverty, so dig in your heels for the quote nutz.",
